Manual overrides for QB invoices/bills that qb_sync.py can't auto-match by DocNumber. Two ways to provide a match:

1. By specific invoice/bill ID (highest priority — exact match):
     invoice_overrides:  {"<QB Invoice Id>": "<project_number>"}
     bill_overrides:     {"<QB Bill Id>":    "<project_number>"}

2. By customer/vendor name pattern (fallback for whole accounts):
     customer_project:   {"<QB Customer name substring>": "<project_number>"}
     vendor_project:     {"<QB Vendor name substring>":   "<project_number>"}

To find the Invoice/Bill Id, open data/qb_status.json and look at the 'unmatched_invoices' and 'unmatched_bills' arrays — each entry has the info you need.
